Btc has come a long way in acceptance the next step will be major items/services priced in btc/eth/ltc directly - not dollars  euros or yen.
Looking at the market caps of these (a slipshot method) it could effect the value of btc maybe 5-10% max & a little higher for eth.
Has anyone calculated how much the price of btc & eth would go down if all ico's were instantly liquidated/dumped ? Maybe they should.
